hadiths[129]{hadithnumber,text}:
2046,"Janab Alqama ka bayan hai ke main Mina mein Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ja raha tha ke unhen Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) miley isliye Usman ne unko alehdgi mein bulaya (aur unko nikah kerney ki targheeb di) lekin Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke unhen nikah ki hajat nahin hai. tab Abdullah ne mujh se kaha : Alqama ! idhar aao . main hazir ho gaya (kyonkey ab takhliye ki zarurat na rahi thi) to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se kaha : aey Abu-Abdur-Rehman ! ( Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) kya ham tumhari eik kanwari ladki se shaadi na kara den? (is tarah ( shayad tumhari ( jawani ki taqat ( phir laut aaye . to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aap ye kehtey hain halanke maine to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai : ''jo tum mein se taqat rakhta ho usey chahiye ke shaadi kar ley . bila-shuba is se nazar neechi aur sharmgaah mehfooz ho jati hai. (damane-iffat par dagh nahin aata.) aur jo taqat na rakhta ho to wo rozey rakhey , ye uskey (shahwaani) jazbaat ko kamzor kar dengey.''"
2047,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurton se chaar baaton ki bina par nikah kiya jata hai. uskey maal , hasab aur nasab, Husn aur jamaal aur uskey deen ki bina par, isliye to dindaar ko ikhtiyar kar , terey haath khaak aalud hon.''"
2048,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : ''kya to ne shaadi kar li hai? '' maine arz kiya : haan ! aapney farmaya : '' kanwari se ya bewa se?'' maine kaha : bewa se. farmaney lagey : ''kanwari se kyon nahin ki ? tum us se kheltey wo tum se khelti.''
2049,"Hamein Fazal-bin Musa ne Husain bin Waqid sey, unhoney Imaara bin Abi Hafsa sey, unhoney Ikrima sey, unhoney, Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kehney laga : meri biwi kisi chhuney waley ka haath radd nahin karti. aapney farmaya : ''usey door kar do (Talaq dey do).'' usney kaha : mujhey andesha hai ke mera dil uskey sath laga rahega . aapney farmaya : ''tab us se fayda uthao.''"
2050,"(A)Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : mujhey eik aurat mili hai jo umda hasab aur Husn aur jamaal wali hai magar uskey aulad nahin hoti . to kya main us se shaadi kar lun? aapney farmaya : ''nahin.'' phir wo dobara aaya, to aapney mana farma diya. phir wo teesri baar aaya to aapney farmaya : ''aisi aurton se shaadi karo jo bahut mohabbat kerney wali aur bahut bachchey janne wali hon. bila-shuba main tumhari kasrat se deegar ummaton par fakhr kerney wala hun. (B) (Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) guzishta hadees ke eik raawi Mustlim bin Saeed ka ta'aruf bayan kartey huey kehtey hain ke) Hasan bin Ali ne bayan kiya ke maine Yazid bin Harun ko suna wo keh rahey they : maine Mustlim ko dekha, wo daain baeyn phirtey rehtey they. Hasan bin Ali ne kaha : unhoney chaalis saal zameen par apna pehlu nahin rakha (na soe). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Mustlim bin Saeed, Mansoor bin Zazan ke bhaanjey ya bhatijey hain. wo sattar din thehrey lekin pani nahin piya."
2051,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Shoaib) se aur wo apney dada (Abdullah bin Amr) se riwayat kartey hain ke Janab Marsad bin Abi Murtad Ghanwi (Raziallahu anhu) Makka se (Musalman) qaidiyon ko utha kar laya kartey they. aur Makka main eik bad-kar aurat thi jis ka naam Anaaq tha aur wo ( qabl az Islam ( uski aashna thi. wo bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main Anaaq se shaadi kar lun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey uska jawab na diya. tab ye aayat kareema nazil hui : (والزانية la ينكحها إلا زان أو مشرك) ''yani bad-kar aurat se koi bad-kar mard ya mushrik hi nikah karta hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bulwaayaa, mujh par ye aayat padhi aur farmaya : ''us se nikah mat karo.''"
2052,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi zaani, jisey zina ki had lagi ho, kisi apney jaisi aurat hi se nikah karta hai. Abu-Ma'mar ne apni sanad mein yun kaha :(حدثني حبيب المعلم  عن  عمرو بن شعيب)."
2053,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apni londi ko azad karkey khud hi us se nikah kar ley, to aisey shakhs ke liye dohra ajr hai.''"
2054,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ko azad farmaya (aur phir apney Haram mein dakhil kerney ka sharf bakhsha) aur unke azad karney hi ko unka haqe-mehar thehraya.
2055,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''raza'at (doodh pilane) ki bina par wo tamam rishtey haram ho jatey hain jo wiladat ke talluq se haram hain.''"
2056,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap meri behan mein raaghib hain? aapney farmaya : ''to kya karun?'' kehney lagin ke aap us se nikah kar lein. aapney farmaya : ''teri behan se?'' bolin : haan. aapney kaha : ''kya tumhen ye pasand hai? '' kehney lagin : main koi aap ke paas akeli to nahin hun. aur is sharaakat mein mujhey ye ziyada pasand hai ke meri behan is khair mein meri hisse-daar baney. aapney farmaya : ''ye merey liye halal nahin hai.'' wo kehney lagin : qasam Allah ki ! mujhey bataya gaya hai ke aapney Darra ya Zarra (hadees ke raawi) Zuhair ko shak hai dukhtar Abu-Salma ke liye paigham bhijwaayaa hai. aapney kaha : ''Umme-Salma ki beti ke liye?'' kehney lagin : haan. aapney farmaya : ''qasam Allah ki ! wo agar meri rabiba na bhi hoti jo ke meri parwarish mein hai, to bhi merey liye halal na ho sakti thi kyonkey wo merey doodh ke bhai ki beti (doodh-shareek bhatiji) hai. mujhey aur uskey walid (Abu-Salma) ko Sobiya ne doodh pilaya tha. so mujhey apni betiyon aur behnon ki pesh-kash mat karo.''"
2057,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Aflah bin Abi Qaiees merey yahan aaye to maine un se parda kiya. unhoney kaha : mujh se parda karti ho, halanke main tumhara chacha hun? kehti hain, maine kaha : kahan se? unhoney kaha : tum ko meri bhawaj ne doodh pilaya hai. kehney lagin : mujhey to aurat ne doodh pilaya hai, mard ne nahin pilaya. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laye to maine aap ko ye baat batai. aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba wo tumhara chacha hai, tumharey paas aa sakta hai.''"
2058,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke yahan aaye to dekha ke unke paas eik aadmi baitha hai. (ba-riwaayat Hafs) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye kaifiyat nagawar guzri aur aap ka chehra badal gaya. (Hafs aur Muhammad bin Kaseer dono ki muttafiqa riwayat hai ke) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne (wazahat kartey huey) kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye mera razaai (doodh shareek) bhai hai. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zara ghaur kar liya karo, tumharey bhai kon hain. doodh pilana wohi moatabar hai jo bhook ki bina par ho.''"
2059,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : '' raza'at (doodh pilana) wohi moatabar hai jo haddiyon ko mazboot karey aur gosht paida karey.'' Abu-Musa ne kaha : tum mein jab tak ye azeem aalim maujud hai ham se mat kuchh puchha karo.
2060,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur lafz (أنشز العظم) zikr kiya.
2061,"Ummahaatul Momenin Hazrat Aaysha aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Abu-Huzaifa bin Utba bin Rabeea bin Abd-Shams ne Salim ko apna munh bola beta banaya hua tha aur us se apni bhatiji Hind dukhtar Waleed bin Utba bin Rabeea ka nikah kar diya tha. wo eik Ansari khatoon ka azad karda ghulam tha jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna munh bola beta banaya tha aur jahiliyat ka ye dastoor tha ke jisey koi apna munh bola beta bana leta to log usko usi ki nisbat se pukara kartey they aur wo (apney munh boley baap ka ( waris bhi banta tha. yahan tak ke Shan Wale Allah ne is baarey mein ye hukm nazil farmaya ke, (ادعوهم لآبائهم إلى فإخوانكم في الدين ومواليكم) ''unhen unke haqeeqi baapon ki nisbat se pukara karo. agar wo maloom na hon to ye tumharey deeni bhai aur maula hain.'' chunanche unhen unke baapon ki taraf lauta diya gaya aur jis ka baap maloom na hua wo maula aur deeni bhai kehlaney laga. gharz ke ! (Abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi) Sehla binte Suhel bin Amr Qarshi, Aamiri (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein) aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham Salim ko apna beta hi samajhtey rahey hain. ye merey aur Abu-Huzaifa ke sath eik hi ghar mein rehta raha hai aur mujhey (ghar mein aam haalat mein) eik kapdey mein dekhta raha hai. (kabhi sar khula, to kabhi pindliyan bhi khul gaeen waghaira.) aur Shan WaleAllah ne aisey logon ke baarey mein jo hukm nazil farmaya hai wo aap jantey hi hain. aap is soorat mein kya farmatey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se kaha : ''usko (apna) doodh pila do.'' chunanche usney usko paanch baar doodh pila diya. aur wo is tarah uskey razaai (doodh shareek) bete ki tarah ho gaya. so Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) us waqia ki bina par apne bhaanjon aur bhateejiyon se kaha karti thin ke falan ko paanch baar doodh pila do. jiskey baarey mein Hazrat Aaysha ki khahish hoti ke wo unko dekh sakey aur unke samney aa sakey. chahey wo badi umr ka bhi hota. chunanche wo iskey baad unke samney aa jaya karta tha. (aur ye us se parda na kartin.) magar Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) aur deegar tamam Ummahaatul Momenin ne isko qubul nahin kiya ke aisi raza'at (doodh pilane) ki bina par koi shakhs unke samney aaye (aur wo us se parda na keren) siwaey iske ke usney paalney mein (do saal ki umr ke dauran mein) doodh piya hota. unhoney Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : qasam Allah ki ! hamein nahin maloom , shayad ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se Salim ke liye ba-muqaabla doosrey logon ko khas rukhsat (chhoot) thi."
2062,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se manqul hai ke Shan Wale Allah ne Quran mein pehley ye nazil kiya tha ke das raza'at se hurmat Sabit hoti hai. (das baar doodh peeney se.) phir usey paanch raza'at se mansookh kar diya. aur jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui to ye alfaz Quran mein qirat kiye jatey they.
2063,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik baar choosnaa ya do baar choosnaa haram nahin karta.''"
2064,"Janab Hujjaj bin Hujjaj apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main doodh pilaney ka haq kis tarah ada kar sakta hun? aapney farmaya : ''eik ghulam ya londi (lekar usey dey dey. Nufaili ne kaha : Hujjaj bin Hujjaj, bano Aslam se talluq rakhta hai aur ye usi ke lafz hain."
2065,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''na nikah ki jaey koi aurat uski phuphi par. na phuphi uski bhatiji par. aur na nikah ki jaey koi aurat uski khaala par. na khaala uski bhaanji par. na nikah ki jaey badi chhoti par aur na chhoti badi par.''"
2066,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is se mana farmaya hai ke aurat aur uski khaala ya aurat aur uski phuphi ko jama kiya jaey.
2067,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney haram kiya is baat ko ke jama ki jaey phuphi aur khaala ya do khalaeyn aur do phuphiyan.
2068,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se aayat kareema (وإن خفتم ألا تقسطوا في اليتمى فانكحوا ما طاب لكم من النساء) ki tafseer daryaft ki . to unhoney kaha : bhaanjey merey ! ye us yateem ladki ke mutalliq hai jo apney kisi wali ki sarparasti mein ho aur (maaldaar ghaniya honey ki wajeh sey) apney wali ke maal mein hissae-daar bin gaee ho. phir us wali ko is ladki ka maal aur jamaal pasand aa jaey aur uski khahish ho ke is se nikah kar ley magar haqe-mehar mein insaf na karey aur is qadr na dena chahey jo koi ghair usey dey, to (aisi soorat mein) un logon ko unke sath nikah se mana kar diya gaya siwaey iske ke un se adl (insaf) keren aur mehar unke aa'laa maiyaar (stendard) ke mutabiq den (to jayez hai). unhen ye hukm diya gaya ke (agar ye andesha ho to) unke alawa deegar aurton se nikah kar lo jo tumhen pasand ayen. Urwa ne kaha : Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke phir logon ne is aayat ke baad jo unke baarey mein utri thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawalat kiye (aur rukhsat chahi) tu Allah taala ne ye nazil farmaya : (ويستفتونك في Nisa قل الله يفتيكم فيهن وما يتلى عليكم في الكتاب في يتمى Nisa التي la تؤتونهن ما كتب لهن w ترغبون أن تنكحوهن) ''aey Paighambar ! log aap se (yateem) aurton ke baarey mein fatwa talab kartey hain. aap un se kahen ke unke baarey mein Allah tumhen fatwa deta hai aur Quran ki wo aayaten bhi (wazahat karti hain) jo tum par un yateem aurton (ladkiyon) ke baarey mein padhi jati hain jinkey muqarrara huqooq (meeras waghaira) tum detey nahin aur un se nikah kerney ki raghbat rakhtey ho.'' Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke ye jo Allah ne zikr kiya hai ke wo tum par kitab mein padhi jati hai, is se murad wo pehley wali aayat hai jis mein Allah taala ne farmaya hai :(وإن خفتم ألا تقسطوا في اليتمى فانكحوا ما طاب لكم من النساء) Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke dusri aayat mein jo aaya hai : (وترغبون أن تنكحوهن) is se murad ''aeraz'' hai. ye aeraz aadmi apni zere-sar-parasti yateem ladki se karta tha jabke wo qaleel-maal na hoti aur Hasan aur jamaal mein bhi maiyaari na hoti. to unhen mana kiya gaya hai ke yateem ladkiyon ke maal aur jamaal ke lalchi bin kar un se nikah mat karo siwaey iske ke adl aur insaf ke taqaazey purey karo (aur ye tafsil nazil honey ki wajeh yehi hai ke log un se aeraz kerney lagey they. Yunus ne bayan kiya ke Janab Rabeea Saar ne (وإن خفتم ألا تقسطوا في اليتمى) ki tauzeeh mein kaha ke Allah farmata hai : ''zulm ka andesha ho to unhen chhod do, maine tumharey liye chaar aurten halal ki hui hain.''"
2069,"Janab ibne-Shahab Zohri se marwi (bayan) hai ke Janab Ali bin Husain (bin Ali bin Abi Talib) ne bayan kiya ke ham log Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki shahadat ke baad Yazid bin Muawiya ke paas se Madina munawwara pahunchey, to mujhey Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) miley aur kaha : merey layaq koi khidmat ho to hukm farmaeyn? maine kaha : nahin. unhoney kaha : kya aap mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki talwaar inayat farma saktey hain? mujhey andesha hai ke uskey mutalliq qaum kahin aap par ghalib na aa jaey. aur qasam Allah ki ! agar aap ye mujhey inayat farma den to merey jeetey ji kabhi koi us tak na pahunch sakega. (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki izzat aur aap ki i'trat ki hifazat aur difaa ham par lazim hai. is silsiley ka eik waqia ye hai ke) Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke hotey huey abu-Jahal ki beti ko shaadi ka paigham bhej diya. maine is silsiley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par khutba detey huey suna jabke main un dino baligh tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Fatima mujh se hai aur mujhey fikr hai ke kahin uskey deen mein koi imtihan na aa jaey.'' phir aapney bani Abd-Shams (bani Umayya) mein se apney daamaad (Hazrat abul-Aas bin Rabee' (Raziallahu anhu)) ka zikr kiya aur uski madah (tareef) farmaee aur khoob farmaee. aapney farmaya : ''usney mujh se baat ki to sachchi ki, wada kiya to pura kiya. main kisi halal ko haram ya haram ko halal nahin karta. lekin qasam Allah ki ! Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti aur Allah ke dushman ki beti kabhi bhi eik jagah jama nahin ho saktin.''"
2070,Maamer ne Zohri se ba-waasta Urwa riwayat kiya aur dusri sanad mein Ayub se ba-waasta ibne-Abi Mulaika (isi tarah) bayan kiya (albatta is riwayat mein ye izafa kiya ke) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) is (doosrey) nikah se khamosh ho gaey.
2071,"Janab Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap member par khadey irshad farma rahey they : ''bani Hisham bin Mughira ne ijazat chahi hai ke Ali bin Abi Talib ko apni beti biyah den. to main iski ijazat nahin deta , phir ijazat nahin deta , phir ijazat nahin deta. haan agar ibne-Abi Talib chahey to meri beti ko Talaq dey dey aur unki ladki se nikah kar ley. bila-shuba meri beti merey dil ka tukda hai. mujhey bura lagta hai jo usey bura lagey. aur mujhey aziyat hoti hai us sey, jis se usko aziyat ho.'' Ahmed bin Yunus ki sanad mein  ''(أخبرنا)'' ka seegha istimal hua hai."
2072,"Zohri (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ham Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ki majlis mein they ke aurton se nikah, mut'aa ka zikr chal pada. to Rabeea bin Sabra naami eik shakhs ne kaha : main apney walid (Sabra) ke mutalliq gawahi deta hun ke unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se Hajjatul-wadaa mein mana farma diya tha."
2073,Rabeea bin Sabra apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurton se mut'aa kerney ko haram farma diya hai.
2074,"Janab Naafe (Rahimahullah) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain : ''Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nikahe-shighaar se mana farmaya hai. ''Musaddad ki riwayat mein ye mazeed hai ke main (Ubaidullah) ne Naafe se puchha ke ''shighaar'' se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha : insan kisi ki beti se nikah karey, aur uskey sath apni beti ka nikah kar dey magar unke beech haq mehar na ho ya insan kisi ki behan se nikah karey aur us se apni behan ka nikah kar dey aur haq mehar na ho."
2075,Abdur-Rehman bin Harmuz Al Aaraj bayan kartey hain ke Abbas bin Abdullah bin Abbas ne Abdur-Rehman bin Hakam se apni beti ka nikah kar diya aur Abdur-Rehman ne apni beti ka nikah un se kar diya aur dono ne us nikah hi ko haqe-mehar thehraya tha. to Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Marwan ko ye hukm likh bheja ke wo unke beech tafriq (farq) kara dey. unhoney apney khat mein kaha ke yehi wo shighaar hai jis se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai.
2076,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''halala kerney wala aur jis ke liye kiya gaya hai (dono) maloon hain.''
2077,Haris Aa'war Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se eik shakhs se riwayat karta hai. ... aur ham samajhtey hain ke wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hain. ... . unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya.
2078,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo ghulam apney Malik ki ijazat ke baghair nikah kar ley wo zaani hai.''"
2079,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jab koi ghulam apney aaqa ki ijazat ke baghair nikah kar ley to uska nikah batil hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye hadees (marfooan) zaeef hai. ye (darasal) moquf hai aur Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka qaul hai.
2080,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi shakhs apney bhai ke paighame-nikah par apna paigham na bhejey.''
2081,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs apney bhai ke paighame-nikah par apna paigham na bhejey aur na apney bhai ke sodey par soda karey magar uski ijazat se.''
2082,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs kisi aurat ko nikah ka paigham bhejey, agar mumkin ho to uski wo cheez dekh ley jo uskey nikah ki daee hai (qad aur qaamat aur Husn aur jamaal waghaira).'' (Hazrat Jabir) kehtey hain ke phir maine eik ladki ke liye nikah ka paigham bheja to main uskey liye chhupa karta tha yahan tak ke maine usey dekh liya jis se mujhey uskey sath nikah kerney ki raghbat hui , chunanche maine us se shaadi kar li."
2083,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aurat ne apney wali ki ijazat ke baghair nikah kiya, uska nikah batil hai. teen baar farmaya. agar shohar us se sohbat kar ley to usko mehar dena padey-ga ba-sabab iskey jo isney us se faayda hasil kiya. agar (waliyon ka ( jhagda ho jaey to haakim wali hai uska jis ka koi wali na ho.''"
2084,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Jaafar bin Rabeea ne Zohri se suna nahin balke (ye hadees) unhoney uski taraf likh bheji thi.
2085,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wali ke baghair koi nikah nahin.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is sanad mein Yunus ne Abu-Barda (Rahimahullah) se. aur Israel ne Abu-Is'haq se aur unhoney Abu'Barda se riwayat ki hai.
2086,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber (Rahimahullah) Ummul-Momenin Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ke mutalliq batatey hain ke ye pehley ibne Jahash ki zojiyat (nikah) mein thin, wo faut ho gaya aur wo un logon mein se tha jo habsha ki janib hijrat karkey gaey they, to Najashi ne unka nikah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kar diya jabkey ye unke yahan (habsha hi mein) thin."
2087,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke meri behan thi , mujhey uskey silsiley mein paigham aatey rahey. mera chacha zaad merey paas aaya to maine uska nikah us se kar diya. magar usney Talaq de-di rajaee Talaq , phir usey chhodey raha yahan tak ke uski iddat khatam ho gaee. phir dobara jab mujhey uskey nikah ke pegham aaye to wo phir merey paas uska paigham lekar aa gaya. maine kaha : qasam Allah ki ! main kabhi bhi tujh se iska nikah nahin karunga . bayan kartey hain ke phir merey hi baarey mein ye aayat kareema nazil hui : (وإذا طلقتم Nisa فبلغن أجلهن فلا تعضلوهن أن ينكحن أزواجهن * * *) ''aur jab tum aurton ko Talaq do , phir wo puri kar lein apni iddat, to na roko unhen is se ke nikah kar lein apney un hi khaawindon sey, jabkey wo aapas mein razi hon dastoor ke muwaafiq. ye nasihat ke jati hai usey jo tum mein se Allah par aur qiyamat ke din par emaan rakhta hai. ye tumharey liye behtar aur pakizah hai. aur Allah janta hai, tum nahin jantey.'' kehtey hain ke phir maine apni qasm ka kaffara ada kiya aur us se nikah kar diya."
2088,Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab do wali kisi aurat ka nikah kar den to ye in mein se pehley waley ke liye hogi. aur jab kisi shakhs ne eik chiz ka do aadmiyon se Sauda kar diya ho to ye pehley waley ki hogi.''
2089,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne aayat kareema (لا يحل لكم أن ترثوا Nisa كرها ولا تعضلوهن) ki tafseer mein farmaya : jab koi aadmi mar jata tha to uskey waris is aurat ke apney wali se bhi ziyada uskey haqdaar bin jatey they. agar un mein se koi chahta to khud hi us se nikah kar leta ya jis se wo chahtey uska nikah kar detey they. aur agar chahtey to uska nikah hi na kartey to is silsiley mein ye aayat nazil hui.
2090,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se aayat kareema : (لا يحل لكم أن ترثوا Nisa كرها ولا تعضلوهن لتذهبوا ببعض ما آتيتموهن إلا أن يأتين بفاحشة مبينة) ki tafseer mein marwi (bayan) hai ke aadmi apney qaribi ki virasat mein uski biwi ka bhi waris bin jata tha aur usey rokey rakhta yahaan tak ke wo mar jati ya usey apna haq mehar wapis karti tu Allah Tabarak w taala ne is amal se mana farma diya.
2091,Ubaidullah (maula Umar) ne Suhaak se uskey ham-maani bayan kiya aur lafz ye they : (فوعظ الله ذلك)  ''Allah ne is baarey mein nasihat farmaee.''
2092,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke bila-shuba Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bewa ka nikah na kiya jaey yahan tak ke us se mashwara kar liya jaey. aur kanwari ka nikah na kiya jaey magar uski ijazat se.'' Sahaba kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! uski ijazat kya hai? aapney farmaya : '' yehi ke khamosh rahey.''
2093,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yateem ladki se (nikah ke silsiley mein) uski apni zaat ke baarey mein mashwara kiya jaey. agar wo khamosh rahey to ye uski ijazat hai aur agar inkar kar dey to us par jabr jayez nahin. Yazid bin Zareea' ki sanad mein ''(أخبرنا)'' ka seegha istimal hua hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Abu-Khalid Sulaiman bin Hayyaan aur Muaz bin Muaz ne Muhammad bin Amr se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai.
2094,"Muhammad bin Amr ne ye hadees apni sanad se riwayat ki aur usney kaha : (فإن بكت أو سكتت) ''agar wo ro padey ya khamosh rahey.'' usney  ''(بكت)'' ke lafz ka izafa kya (ro padey). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye lafz ''(بكت)'' mehfooz nahin, weham hai jo ibne Idrees se hua hai ya Muhammad bin Ala se. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Abu-Amr Zakwaan ne Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kiya, wo kehti hain ke (maine kaha :) aey Allah ke Rasool ! kanwari ladki to baat kerney se haya karti hai. aapney farmaya : ''uska khamosh rehna hi uska iqrar hai.''"
2095,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se waarid hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ladkiyon ke silsiley mein aurton se (unki maaon sey) mashwara kar liya karo.''"
2096,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik jawan kunwari ladki Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai. usney bataya ke uskey baap ne uski shaadi kar di hai magar main usey napasand karti hun. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey ikhtiyar dey diya.
2097,"Ikrima Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi riwayat bayan kartey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke (Ikrima ne) ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka naam zikr nahin kiya, aur muhaddeseen ke yahan is riwayat ko isi tarah mursal riwayat karna hi maroof hai."
2098,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bewa apni zaat ke baarey mein apney wali ki ba-nisbat ziyada haqdaar hai. aur kunwari se bhi uskey apney baarey mein mashwara kiya jaey, uski ijazat iski khamoshi hai.'' aur ye lafz Qaanabi ( Abdullah bin Muslima) ke hain."
2099,"Abdullah bin Fazal ne apni sanad se aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya aur kaha : ''bewa apney wali ki ba-nisbat , apney baarey mein ziyada haq daar hai. aur kunwari se uska baap mashwara karey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain (أبوها) ''uska baap'' ka lafz mehfooz nahin."
2100,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wali ko bewa ke maamley mein koi dakhal hasil nahin hai. aur yateem ladki se mashwara kiya jaey aur uski khamoshi uska iqrar hai.''"
2101,Hazrat Khansa binte Khizaam Ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke uskey walid ne uski shaadi kar di jabkey wo bewa thi. usney ye nikah napasand kiya aur phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur aap ke samney uska zikr kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska nikah radd kar diya. (fasakh kar diya.)
2102,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat hai ke Abu Hind ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sar mein seengi lagai. aur phir aapney farmaya : ''aey bani Biyaaza ! Abu Hind ka (apney mein se kisi ke sath) nikah kar do. aur us se (us ki kisi Azeeza ka ( nikah ley lo.'' aur farmaya : ''agar tumhari dawaaon mein se kisi mein khair hai to wo seengi laganey hi mein hai. ''
2103,"Memuna binte Kardam (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main apney walid ke sath chali, us hajj ke mauqe par jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hajj kya to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, merey walid unke qarib huey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni oontni par they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki khatir ruk gaey, merey walid ne aap se faaydemand baaten sunin. aap ke paas darra tha jaisey ke muallim logon ke paas hota hai. maine badviyon ko aur logon ko suna ke wo keh rahey they : (الطبطبية , الطبطبية , الطبطبية) (chaltey huey paon padney ki aawaz. tibb tibb. ya kudra (kodaa) maarney ki aawaz) merey walid aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qarib huye, aap ke qadam Mubarak pakad liye , aap ki risaalat ka iqrar kiya, aap ke paas khadey rahey aur aap ke irshaadaat suney. merey walid ne bataya ke main lashkare-ishraan mein shareek hua tha. ibne Musanna ne isko ghasraan kaha : (ghain manqoot (nuqate) ke sath ( (ye daure-jahiliyat ki eik jang ka waqia hai.) is dauran mein Tariq bin Muraqqa'a ne kaha tha : kon hai jo mujhey apna neza dey aur uska badla paey? maine kaha : uska badla kya hai? kaha : main uskey sath apni is beti ka nikah kar dunga jo sab se pehley paida hogi . chunanche maine usko apna neza dey diya, phir us se ghayeb raha yahan tak ke mujhey ilm hua ke uskey yahaan ladki paida hui hai aur ab baligh ho chuki hai. phir main uskey paas gaya , aur us se kaha ke merey ghar walon (meri banney wali biwi) ko meri taraf tayyar kar do. to usney qasam uthai ke wo aisa nahin kerega yahan tak ke main usey naya mehar pesh karun, ba-khilaaf uskey jo merey aur uskey darmiyan ho chuka tha. aur maine bhi qasam utha li ke jo dey chuka hun bas wohi hai aur nahin dunga . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''aur ab wo ladki kis umr mein hai? kaha ke ab to uskey baalon mein safedi aa gaee hai.'' aapney farmaya : ''mera khayal hai ke to usey chhod dey.'' aap ki ye baat mujhey pareshan kar gaee . aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf dekha. jab aapney meri ye kaiyfiyat dekhi to farmaya : ''na tum gunah-gaar bano aur na tumhara sathi gunah-gaar baney.'' Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain, (القتير) ka maani baalon ki safedi (budhapa) hai."
2104,"Ibrahim bin Maisraa ne bayan kiya ke uski khaala ne eik khatoon se khabar sunai jo kamaal ki sachchi aurat thi, wo bayan karti thi ke daure-jahiliyat mein merey walid eik jang mein gaey. un logon ko garmi lagney lagi to eik shakhs ne kaha : kon hai jo mujhey apney jootey dey-dey , main uska apni pehli paida honey wali beti se nikah kar dun ga. chunanche merey baap ne apney jootey utaar kar uski taraf phenk diye. phir uskey yahaan ladki paida hui , aur baligh ho gaee . aur guzishta qisse ki manind bayan kiya magar safedi zahir honey ka zikr nahin kiya."
2105,Abu-Salma kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haq mehar ke baarey mein puchha to unhoney bataya ke baara auqiya aur nash. maine kaha : nash kya hai? unhoney kaha : aadha auqiya.
2106,"Abul-Ajfa'a Sulmi kehtey hain ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein khutba diya aur kaha : ''khabrdar ! aurton ke silsiley mein bhari bhari mehar mat baandha karo, agar ye cheez duniya mein izzat aur Allah ke yahan taqwe ka sabut hoti to is mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sab se badh kar hotey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni kisi biwi aur apni saahibzaadiyon mein se kisi ko baara auqiya se ziyada mehar nahin diya.''"
2107,Ummul-Momenin Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ( apney mutalliq ( bayan karti hain ke ye pehley Ubaidullah bin Jahash ki zojiyat (nikah) mein thin aur wo habsha ja kar faut ho gaya to Najashi ne unki shaadi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath kar di aur apni taraf se unko chaar hazar (dirham) mehar ada kiye. phir unhen Shurahbeel bin Hasna (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhej diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) wazahat farmatey hain ke Shurahbeel bin Hasna mein ''Hasana'' unki walida ka naam hai.
2108,"Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) ka bayan hai ke Najashi ne Umme-Habiba binte-Abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anha) ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se nikah kar diya, aur chaar hazar dirham mehar ada kiye. aur ye khabar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko likh bheji to aapney isey qubul farma liya."
2109,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) par Zaafran ke nishaanaat dekhay . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''ye kya hai? '' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine eik aurat se shaadi kar li hai. aapney daryaft farmaya : '' mehar kitna diya hai? ''kaha ke guthli ke wazan ke barabar sona . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' waleema karo agar-che eik bakri hi ka ho.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : eik nawaah ( guthli ( paanch dirham ke barabar hoti hai aur nash bees dirham ka aur auqiya chaalis dirham ka .
2110,"Musa bin Muslim bin Rumaan, abu-Zubair sey, wo Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anha) se naqal kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi aurat ko mehar mein do haath bhar kar sattu dey diye ya khajoor, usney usko halal kar liya.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke us riwayat ko Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ne Saleh bin Rumaan sey, unhoney abu-Zubair sey, unhoney Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se moquf riwayat kya hai. aur abu-Aasim ne Saleh bin Rumaan se unhoney abu-Zubair se unhoney Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat mein kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein ham eik mutthi tuaam par mutaa kar liya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : usko ibne-Juraij ne b-waasta abu-Zubair , Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se abu-Aasim ki tarah bayan kya."
2111,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main apney aap ko aap ki khidmat mein hiba karti hun, aur phir wo bahut der khadi rahi. tab eik aadmi utha aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar aap ko us mein raghbat nahin to uski shaadi mujh se kar dijiye . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas kuch hai jo usey mehar ke taur par dey sako ?'' kehney laga : merey paas to bas ye teh band hi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum agar apna teh band usko dey dogey to khud teh band ke baghair beth rahogey , koi aur chiz dhoondo .'' kehney laga : merey paas to aur kuch nahin hai. aapney farmaya : '' dhoond lao chahey lohey ka chhalla hi ho.'' usney talash kya magar usey kuch na mila . tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha : ''kya tumhen Quran se kuch yaad hai? '' kehney laga : haan , falan falan suraten . usney unke naam liye . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us Quran ke iwaz , jo tumhen yaad hai, main uska nikah tumharey sath karta hun. ''"
2112,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi qisse ki manind zikr kya. magar us mein tehband aur chhalley ka zikr nahin hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha : ''tujhey Quran kis qadr yaad hai? '' usney kaha : sura baqara ya uskey sath wali . aapney farmaya : '' jao, usey bees aayaten padha do aur ye tumhari biwi hui .''"
2113,Muhammad bin Rashid ne Mak-hool se Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat ki manind bayan kya. Mak-hool kaha kartey they ke ye amal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad kisi aur ke liye munasib nahin hai.
2114,"Janab Masruq (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se masla puchha gaya ke eik shakhs ne kisi aurat se shaadi ki, phir wafat pa gaya jabkey unka milaap na hua tha aur na haq mehar hi muqarrar kya tha (to us soorat mein kya hukm hai?) unhoney farmaya : us aurat ke liye pura mehar hai, us par iddat lazim hai aur ye virasat ki bhi haq daar hai. (tab) Maaqil bin Sanan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ( aisey hi) suna tha aapney Baro bint Washiq ke baarey mein yehi faisla farmaya tha."
2115,Usman bin abi Sheba apni sanad se Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se usi tarah riwayat kartey hain.
2116,"Abdullah bin Utba bin Masood , Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs ke baarey mein Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko yehi khabar di gaee . aur phir wo log eik mahina tak unke paas chakkar lagatey rahey . ya kaha kaee baar unke paas aaye . to bil-aakhir ye kaha : meri raey us mein ye hai ke ye aurat mehar ki haqdaar hai jaisey ke is tarah ki aurton ka haq mehar hota hai) mehar misl ( baghair kisi kami beshi ke . aur ye meeras ki haqdaar hai aur us par iddat ( wafat ( bhi lazim hai. agar meri ye baat haq aur durust hai tu Allah ki janib se hai aur agar ghalat hai to meri taraf se hai aur shetan ki taraf sey, Allah aur uskey Rasool dono us se buri hain. chunanche qabeela Ashja ke log khadey huey un mein Jarrah aur abu-Sanaan bhi they, unhoney kaha : aey ibne-Masood! ham gawahi detey hain ke yehi faisla Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamari eik aurat Birwa binte-Washiq aur uskey shohar Hilal bin Murra Ashjai ke baarey mein farmaya tha, jaisey ke aapney kya hai. raawi ne bayan kya ke us se Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko behad khushi hui ke unka faisla Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke faisley ke mutabiq hua hai."
2117,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs se kaha : ''kya tum razi ho ke falan aurat se tumhari shaadi kar dun ?'' usney kaha : ji haan : phir aapney aurat se puchha : ''kya to razi hai ke falan mard se teri shaadi kar dun ?'' to usney kaha : ji haan ! chunanche aapney un dono ki shaadi kar di. aur phir us mard ne us se sohbat ki magar haq mehar muqarrar na kya aur na usey kuch diya. aur ye un logon mein se tha jo Hudebiya mein shareek ho chukey they aur Shurkaaye Hudebiya ko khaibar mein hissey mila tha. jab uski wafat ka waqt aaya to usney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne falan aurat se meri shaadi kar di thi magar maine uskey liye mehar muqarrar nahin kya tha aur na usey kuch diya tha, aur main tumhen gawah banata hun ke main usey mehar mein apna khaibar ka hissa deta hun. chunanche us aurat ne wo hissey liya aur phir usey eik lakh mein bech diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadees ke shuru mein itna izafa kya. ... aur uski hadees ziyada kamil hai. ... kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''behtareen nikah wohi hai jo ziyada aasani wala ho.'' aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aadmi se kaha . ... . uskey baad mazkura baala hadees ki manind hadees bayan ki . Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : andesha hai ke hadees mulhiq hai kyonkey Amr waqia uskey khilaf hai."
2118,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen khutbae-hajat taaleem farmaya wo ye ke (إن الحمد لله نستعينه ونستغفره ونعوذ به من شرور أنفسنا . .  ۔) ''tamam tareefen Allah ke liye hain. ham usi se madad chahtey hain. aur (apney gunahon ki) maafi chahtey hain aur apney nafson ki shararaton se uski panah chahtey hain. jisey wo raahe-haq sujha dey koi usey gumrah nahin kar sakta, aur jisey wo gumraah kar dey uskey liye koi raahnuma nahin ho sakta. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Allah azz-w-jall ke siwa aur koi mabud bar-haq nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' aey logo jo emaan laye ho ! Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karo jiskey wastey se tum sawal kartey ho, aur rishtey natey ( todney ( se bacho , bila-shuba Allah taala tum par nigehban hai.'' ''aey emaan walo! Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karo aur us se daro jaisey ke usse darney ka haq hai aur tum par maut na aaye magar is haal mein ke tum musalman ho.'' ''aey emaan walo! Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karo aur baat hamesha saaf sidhi kya karo . Allah taala tumharey aamaal durust farma dega , tumhari khataeyn maaf kar dega, aur jisney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat kar li bila-shuba wo azeem kamiyabi se hamkinaar hua . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Muhammad bin Suleman ne ( shuru riwayat mein) lafz ( أن ( zikr nahin kya."
2119,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab khutba padhtey . ... . to guzishta hadees ke misl zikr kya. aur (محمدا عبده ورسوله) ke baad ye kehtey ( أرسله بالحق بشيرا ونذيرا بين يدي الساعة ، من يطع الله ورسوله فقد رشد ، ومن يعصھما فإنه لا يضر إلا نفسه ولا يضر الله شيئا) ''Allah ne unko haq de-kar khushkhabri deney wala aur daraney wala bana kar bheja ke qiyamat se pehley pehley logon ko mutanabbeh kar den. jisney bhi Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat ki wo yaqinan hidayat pa gaya aur jisney unki nafarmani ki usney apna hi nuqsan kya, wo Allah ka koi nuqsan nahin kar sakta. ''"
2120,"Ismael bin Ibrahim , bano Sulaim ke eik shakhs se riwayat kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se amaama bint abdul-Muttalib ka rishta talab kya to aapney uska mujh se nikah kar diya aur khutba bhi na padha . hamen abu-Esa ne bataya ke Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) se puchha gaya : kya ye jayez hai? unhoney kaha : haan , us baarey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ahadis aati hain."
2121,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se shaadi ki to us waqt meri umr saat saal thi. Suleman ne kaha : ya chhe saal. aur mujh se milaap hua (main aap ke ghar bheji gaee) to main no saal ki thi.
2122,"ummul-momenin Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se shaadi ki to aap ( shuru dinon mein) unke yahan teen din thehrey , phir farmaya : ''tum apney ghar walon par koi be qadr w qeemat nahin ho. agar chaho to main tumharey liye saat din ruk jata hun. lekin agar tumharey yahan saat din thehra , to deegar azwaaj ke yahan bhi saat saat hi din thahrunga.''"
2123,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safiya ( binte-Huyi ( ko ley liya ( shaadi kar li ( to unke yahan teen din iqaamat ki . Usman bin abi Sheba ne mazeed kaha ke wo bewa thin . aur unhoney kaha : ( حدثني هشيم  , أخبرنا حميد  : أخبرنا أنس ( ."
2124,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar koi shakhs ( apney yahan ( bewa ( biwi (ke hotey huey kanwari se shaadi karey to uskey haan saat din rukey . aur jab bewa se shaadi karey to uskey haan teen din .) abu-Qulaba ne ( kaha : agar main kahun ke unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansoob karkey ( marfoo ( bayan kya to main sach hi kahunga , lekin unhoney kaha tha : '' sunnat yehi hai. ''"
2125,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jab Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) se shaadi ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : '' usko koi chiz do .'' unhoney kaha : ''merey paas to koi chiz nahin hai. '' aapney farmaya : '' wo tumhari hutami zireh kahan hai? ''
2126,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sahaba mein se eik shakhs se riwayat hai ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne jab Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti se shaadi ki aur unke yahan jana chaha , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko rok liya yahan tak ke pehley koi chiz pesh karen. unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey paas koi chiz nahin hai. aapney farmaya : '' apni zireh hi dey do .'' chunanche unhoney unko apni zireh di , phir unke yahan gaey ."
2127,Ikrima (Rahimahullah) Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se uski misl riwayat kartey hain.
2128,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke kisi aurat ko uskey shohar par pesh na karun jab tak ke wo usko koi chiz na dey dey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke khaisma (bin Abdur-Rehman Jaafi ( ne Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se nahin suna hai.
2129,"Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Shoaib) sey, wo ( apney ( dada ( Abdullah bin Amr ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aurat ka kisi se nikah ho aur aqd nikah se pehley jo koi mehar , Atiya ya wada kya gaya ho to wo sab us aurat ka haq hai. aur jo aqd ke baad diya jaey to wo usi ka hai jis ko diya jaey. aur kisi ka sab se umda ikram wo hai jo uski beti ya behan ki wajeh se kya jaey.''"
2130,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu alaihi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi ko uski shaadi ki Mubarak baad dete, to farmatey :  (بارك الله لك ، و بارك عليك وجمع بينكما في خير) ''Allah tumhein barkat dey , tum par apni barkat farmaai aur tum dono ko khair ke sath ikhatta rakhey .''"
2131,"Basra naami eik sahabi se riwayat hai usney kaha : maine eik kanwari ladki se shaadi ki, jo ke apney pardey mein thi. main us par dakhil hua to wo hamila thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' usko haq mehar milega b-wajah uskey jo to ne uski sharmgaah ko halal jana aur bacha tera ghulam hoga , jab ye bacha jan ley.'' bilfaaz Hasan bin Ali . ... '' to usey durrey laga.'' aur bilfaaz ibne-abi al-Sarq. ... ''tum log usko durrey lagao ya kaha ke usko had lagao. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Qatada ne b-waasta Saeed bin Yazid , ibn Musaiyab se aur Yahya bin abi kaseer ne b-waasta Yazid bin Nuaim, Saeed bin Musaiyab se aur Ata khuraasaani ne Saeed bin Musaiyab se riwayat ki aur sab ne usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal hi riwayat kya hai. Yahya bin abi kaseer ki riwayat mein hai ke Basra bin Aksam ne eik aurat se nikah kya aur tamam raviyon ne kaha ke aapney bachey ko uska ghulam qarar diya."
2132,"Yahya bin abi kaseer ne Yazid bin Nueim se unhoney Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se riwayat kya ke eik shakhs ne , jisey Basra bin Aksam kaha jata tha, eik aurat se nikah kya. ... . aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya. ... . aur izafa kya ke unke beech tafriq kar di. aur ibne-Juraij ki riwayat ziyada kamil hai."
2133,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jis shakhs ki do biwiyan hon aur phir wo kisi eik ki taraf maael ho gaya to wo qiyamat ke roz us keyfiyat mein aaeyga ke uska eik pehlu jhuka hua hoga .''
2134,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (apni pak biviyon ke beech) taqseem kartey aur adl kartey aur farmaya kartey : ''aey Allah! ye meri taqseem hai jo merey bas mein hai. aur is baat mein mujhey malamat na farmana jis ka to Malik hai aur mera us par ikhtiyar nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is se murad dil (ka mailan) hai.
2135,"Urwa (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aey merey bhaanjey! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ham azwaaj mein) baari muqarrar kerney ke maamley mein, yani hamarey paas theherney ke maamley mein ham mein se kisi ko kisi par fazilat na diya kartey they. aur aap taqreeban her roz ham sab ke paas chakkar lagaya kartey they aur her biwi ke qarib hotey. ye nahin ke aap sohbat kartey they. yahan tak ke uskey paas ja pahunchtey jiski baari ka din hota aur raat uskey yahan guzaarey. Hazrat Sauda binte-Zamaa (Raziallahu anha) jab badi umr ki ho gaeen aur unhen andesha hua ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen chhod dengey to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! mera din Aaisha ke liye (waqf) hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey qubul farma liya. (Hazrat Aaisha) kehti hain ke ham kaha karti thin ke usi silsile mein aur usi qism ki soorate-ahwaal ke mutalliq hi Allah azz-w-jall ne ye aayat nazil farmai hai : (وإن امرأة خافت من بعلها نشوزا) ''agar kisi aurat ko andesha ho apney khawind ke bigadne ka.''"
2136,"Muaza, Hazrat Aeysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat karti hain unka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sura ehzaab ki aayat kareema : (ترجي من تشاء منهن وتؤوي إليك من تشاء) ke nazil ho janey ke baad) bhi) ham mein se jiski baari ka din hota us se ijazat liya kartey they ( jab kisi doosrey Haram mein janey ki koi zarurat hoti .) Muaza kehti hain maine Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kya kaha karti thin ? unhoney kaha : main kaha karti thi : agar ye faisla karna merey hi zimmey hai to phir main apney aap par kisi aur ko tarjeeh nahin dey sakti ."
2137,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni pak biviyon ko bulwaya. yani apney marze-wafat ke dino mein , to wo jama ho gaeen , aapney farmaya : ''main ab tumharey darmiyan chakkar nahin laga sakta agar munasib samjho aur mujhey ijazat dey do , to main Aaisha ke yahan reh lun .'' to sab ne ijazat dey di."
2138,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi safar ka irada farmatey to apni pak biviyon mein qura daltey , jis ka naam nikal aata wo aap ke sath safar mein jati . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her zauja ko uski baari ka din aur raat detey , siwaye Hazrat Sauda bint Zamaa (Raziallahu anha) ke , unhoney apna din Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko hiba kar diya tha."
2139,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' sharton mein se aham tareen shart jis ka pura karna tum par wajib hai, wo hai jiski bina par tum ne (biwiyon ki) ismaton ko halal kya ho.''"
2140,"Hazrat Qais bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Haira gaya, to maine dekha ke wo log apney sardar ko sajda kartey hain to maine kaha : Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is baat ke ziyada haqdaar hain ke unko sajda kya jaey. kehtey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur bataya ke main Haira gaya, to dekha ke wo log apney sardar ko sajda kartey hain to aap aey Allah ke Rasool ! is baat ke ziyada haqdaar hain ke ham aap ke samney sajda rez hon. aapney farmaya : ''bhala bata ke agar to meri qabr par guzarta to kya usey sajda karta?'' maine kaha ke nahin. aapney farmaya : ''to aisa na karo. agar main kisi ko sajda kerney ka kehta to aurton ko hukm deta ke apney shohron ko sajda keren kyonkey Allah taala ne biwi par shohar ka bahut haq rakha hai. ''"
2141,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab shohar biwi ko apney bistar par bulaey aur wo na aaye aur shohar ghussey mein raat guzar dey to farishtey us biwi par subh honey tak lanat kartey rehtey hain. ''"
2142,"Janab Hakim bin Muawiya qushairi apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham par biwi ke kya huqooq hain? aapney farmaya : ''jab to khaye to usey khilaaey, jab to pehney to usey pahnaaey.'' ya yun kaha : ''jab kama kar laye ( to usey pahnaaey (aur chehrey par na maar , bura na bol aur us se juda na ho magar ghar mein .'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain (ولا تقبح) ke maani hain : '' yun mat kaho ke Allah tujhey qabeeh bana dey.''"
2143,"Behaz bin Hakim apney walid ( hakim ( sey, wo ( uskey ( dada ( Muawiya bin Haida qushairi (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham apni biwiyon se kis tarah faeyda uthaeyn aur kya choden ? aapney farmaya : '' apni kheti ko aa jaisey to chahey, usey khila jab to khaye, usey pehna jab to pehney, chehrey ke qabeeh honey ki bad dua (ya gaali) na dey aur (munh par) mat maar. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Shoba ki riwayat mein hai : ( طعمها إذا طعمت وتكسوها إذا اكتسيت)."
2144,"Hazrat Muawiya Qusheiri (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : aap ( hamen ( hamari aurton ke baarey mein kya irshad farmatey hain? aapney farmaya : ''jo khatey ho us se unhen khilao , jo pehantey ho us se unhen pehnao , unhen maaro nahin aur qabeeh honey ki gaali (ya bad dua ( na do .''"
2145,Abu-Harra Raqashi apney chacha se bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tumhen un se nafarmani ka andesha ho to unhen bistaron se alehda kar do. Hammad ne kaha : is se murad mubashrat hai. ( ham-bistari na karo .)
2146,"Ayas bin Abdullah bin Ubai Zubab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki bandiyon ko mat maara karo .'' to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur kaha : aurten apney shohron ke sar chadhney lagi hain. pas aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko maarney ki rukhsat dey di. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar walon ke paas aurten bahut ziyada aaney lagin jo apney shohron ki shikayat karti thin . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar walon ke paas aurten bahut ziyada aai hain jo apney shohron ki shikayat karti hain. aisey log koi achey aadmi nahin hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne hamen kaha ke Zohri ke Shekh ka naam Abdullah bin Abdullah hi hai) na ke Ubaidullah .)"
2147,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shohar sey, biwi ko maarney ke silsiley mein, sawal nahin kya jaeyga.''"
2148,Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah bijli (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se achcha nazar pad janey ke mutalliq puchha to aapney farmaya : ''apni nazar pher lo.''
2149,"ibn Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''aey Ali! nazar ke peechey nazar mat lagao, pehli tumharey liye maaf hai (jo achcha pad gaee) dusri nahin (umda dekhna.'')"
2150,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi aurat kisi dusri aurat ke sath baghal geer ho kar ya chimat kar na letey aur phir apney shohar ko uskey mutalliq bataaney lagey goya wo uski taraf dekh raha hai.''
2151,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne koi aurat dekhi phir ( apney ghar ( Hazrat Zenab bint Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aaye aur un se apni hajat puri ki . phir apney as-haab ke paas gaey aur un se farmaya : '' aurat shetan ki soorat mein samney aati hai, jo shakhs is tarah ki koi keyfiyat mehsoos karey to usey chahiye ke apni biwi ke paas chala jaey, bila-shuba ( biwi ke paas jana ( uskey nafs mein aaney waley waswasey aur khayal ko nikal dega .''"
2152,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke (لمم) ( chhotey motey gunahon ( ki tafseer mein , maine Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat se badh kar aur koi chiz nahin dekhi . Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se naqal kartey hain : ''Allah taala ne ibne-Adam par zina se uska hissey likh diya hai jisey wo pa kar rahega. to aakhon ka zina dekhna hai, zaban ka zina bolnaa hai, aur dil tamanna aur khahish karta hai aur sharmgaah uski tasdeeq ya takzeeb karti hai. ''"
2153,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''har Adam zaad ke liye zina se uska hissey ( likha gaya ( hai. aur mazkura qissa bayan kiya, kaha : '' haath zina kartey hain, inki bad-kari , pakadna hai. paon zina kartey hain, inki bad-kari , chalna hai. munh zina karta hai aur uski bad-kari , bosa lena hai.''"
2154,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura qissa bayan kiya. farmaya : ''kaan zina kartey hain aur unki bad-kari, sunna hai.''"
2155,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hunain ke mauqe par Autas ki taraf eik muhim bheji , wo apney dushman se muqabil huye, un se jang ki, un par ghalib rahey aur unki aurten haath aain to kuchh as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se mubashrat mein harj jana kyonkey mushrekin mein unke shohar maujud they. tu Allah taala ne is silsiley mein ye aayat utaari : (والمحصنات من Nisa إلا ما ملكت أيمانكم) ''aur khaawindon waliyan (tum par haram hain) magar jinkey Malik bin jaeyn tumharey dahiney haath.'' yani wo tumharey liye halal hain jab unki iddat puri ho jaey."
2156,Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik ghazwey main eik aurat dekhi jis ka hamal taqreeban purey dino ka tha. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shayad uskey Malik ne us se mubashrat ki hai?'' unhoney kaha : ji haan. aapney farmaya : ''maine irada kiya hai ke usey lanat karun aisi lanat jo uski qabr tak uskey sath jaey. ye us bachchey ko kis tarah apna waris bana sakega jabkey uskey liye ye halal nahin (ke ghair ke nutfey aur ghair ke bachchey ko apna bachcha banaey) aur kyonkar is se (ghulamon ki tarah) khidmat ley sakega jabkey ye iskey liye halal nahin.'' (agar bil-farz uska apna nutfa hua aur apney bete ke nasab ka inkar kiya to ye haram hai. aur phir bete ko ghulam aur khaadim ke darjay par utaarna kyonkar jayez hai?)
2157,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf nisbat kartey huey bayan kiya ke aapney Autas mein pakdi janey wali aurton ke baarey mein farmaya tha : '' kisi hamila se mubashrat na ki jaey yahan tak ke uskey bachchey ki wiladat ho jaey aur ghair hamila se bhi mubashrat na ki jaey yahan tak ke usey eik haiz aa jaey.''
2158,"Hansh San'aani (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ruwefe bin Sabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ham mein khutbe ke liye khadey huey to kaha : main tumhen wohi baat kahunga jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hai. aapney hamein Hunain waley din farmaya tha : ''jo shakhs Allah aur yoame-aakhirat (ke din) par emaan rakhta hai uskey liye halal nahin ke kisi doosrey ki kheti ko apna pani dey.'' aap ki murad thi ke hamila aurton se mubashrat '' aur jo shakhs Allah aur yoame aakhirat par emaan rakhta hai uskey liye halal nahin ke qaid mein aaney wali kisi aurat se istibraa (reham saaf honey) se pehley mubashrat karey, aur jo shakhs Allah aur yoame aakhirat par emaan rakhta hai uskey liye halal nahin ke ghanimat ko taqseem ho janey se pehley farokht karey.''"
2159,"Saeed bin Mansoor , Abu-Muaawia sey, wo ibne Is-haq se ye hadees bayan kartey hain, kaha ke ''yahan tak ke eik haiz se uska istibraa (reham saaf) na kar ley.'' is mein (بحيضة) ka lafz ziyada kiya jo ke Abu-Muaawia ka weham hai magar abu-Saeed ki riwayat mein sahih hai. aur us mein mazeed ye hai : ''jo shakhs Allah aur yoame aakhirat par emaan rakhta hai wo musalmanon ke maale ghanimat ke janweron mein se kisi par Sawar na ho ke jab usey kamzor kar dey to usey wapis kar dey . aur jo Allah aur yoame aakhirat par emaan rakhta hai wo musalmanon ke maale ghanimat ke kapdon mein se koi kapda na pehney ke jab usey puraanaa kar dey to wapis kar dey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (الحيضة) ka lafz mehfooz nahin hai aur ye Abu-Muaawia ka weham hai."
2160,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Shoaib) se aur wo apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi kisi aurat se shaadi karey ya koi khaadim khareedey to chahiye ke ye dua karey : ''(اللهم ! إني أسألك خيرها وخير ما جبلتها عليه ، وأعوذبك من شرها ومن شر ما جبلتها عليه)'' ''aey Allah ! main iski khair ka sawal karta hun aur us khair ka jis par to ne isko paida kiya, aur iskey shar se teri panah maangta hun aur us shar se jis par to ne isko paida kiya hai.'' aur jab koi oont khareedey to uskey kohan ki choti ko pakdey aur isi tarah dua karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abu-Saeed ne izafa kiya ke (aapney farmaya :) ''biwi aur khaadim ki peshani ke baal pakdey aur barkat ki dua karey.''"
2161,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi jab apni ehliya se mubashrat ka irada karey aur nichey likhi dua padh ley to agar un mein is baari mein bachcha muqaddar hua to usey shaitan kabhi nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakega. (dua ye hai) (بسم الله اللهم ! جنبنا الشيطان وجنب الشيطان ما رزقتنا) ''Allah ke naam sey, aey Allah ! ham ko shaitan se door rakh , aur shaitan ko is se door rakh jo to hamen inayat farmaey.''"
2162,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mal'oon hai wo shakhs jo biwi se peeth mein mubashrat karta hai.''"
2163,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke yahudi kaha kartey they ke agar aadmi apni biwi se uskey peechhey se sharmgaah (pahle) mein mubashrat karey (ke wo pet ke bal leti hui ho) to us se bachcha bhengaa paida hota hai, to Shan waley Allah  ne ye nazil farmaya : (نساؤكم حرث لكم فأتوا حرثكم أنى شئتم) ''tumhari aurten tumhari khetiyan hain, apne kheton mein jaisey chaho aao.''"
2164,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai, unhoney kaha : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki Allah maghfirat farmaai . unhen weham hua hai. darasal qabeela ansaar but parast log they, us yahudi qabiley ke sath rehtey they jo ke ehle-kitab they. aur ansaar ilm ki wajeh se unki fazilat ke moa'trif they aur apney aksar kamon mein unki perwi kiya kartey they. ehle-kitab ka mamla ye tha ke ye log apni biwiyon se eik hi andaz mein chit litaa kar (ya pehlu ke bal sey) mujaamiat (sambhog) kiya kartey they. is tarah aurat bahut ziyada pardey mein rehti hai. in Ansariyon ne bhi un jaisa ye amal ikhtiyar kiya hua tha. lekin qabeela Quraish waley apni aurton ko buri tarah phailatey they aur tarah tarah se mutalazzaz hotey (lazzat lete) they. aagey sey, peechhey se aur chit litaa kar. jab muhajrin Madiney mein aaye aur unke eik aadmi ne ansaar ki eik aurat se shaadi ki to uskey sath apney usi andaz mein sohbat kerney laga to aurat ne bahut bura jana aur kehney lagi : ham se eik hi andaz mein (chit litaa kar ya pehlu ke bal sey) sohbat ki jati thi, so tum bhi isi tarah karo warna mujh se alag raho yahan tak ke unka mamla bahut badh gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak ja pahuncha. tu Allah taala ne ye nazil farmaya : (نساؤكم حرث لكم فأتوا حرثكم أنى شئتم) ''tumhari aurten tumhari khetiyan hain, to apni kheti mein jis tarah se ji chahey aao.'' aagey sey, peechhey se ya chit litaa kar , lekin jagah wohi bachchey wali ho."
2165,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke yahudi log jab un mein koi aurat haiz se hoti to usko ghar se nikal detey they. uskey sath khatey na peetey aur na eik ghar mein ikhattey rehtey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is baarey mein puchha gaya tu Allah taala ne ye nazil farmaya : (ويسألونك an المحيض قل هو أذى فاعتزلوا Nisa في المحيض . .  . ۔)  ''log aap se haiz ke baarey mein sawal kartey hain, keh dijiye ke wo gandagi hai, so haalate haiz mein aurton se alag raho. ...'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unke sath gharon mein ikhattey raho aur har kaam kar saktey ho siwaye nikah (jinsi amal) ke.'' yahudi kehney lagey : ye aadmi (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) hamarey kisi kaam ko nahin chhodta magar uski mukhalifat hi karta hai. Hazrat Usaid bin Huzair aur Ibad bin Bishr (Raziallahu Anhuma) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! yahudi is is tarah kehtey hain, to kya ham haiz ke dino mein bhi aurton se mujaamiat (sambhog) na kar liya keren? is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak badal gaya. yahan tak ke hamein yaqeen ho gaya ke aap un dono se haqiqat mein naraz ho gaey hain, chunanche wo (aap ki majlis sey) nikal aaye. (unke janey ke baad) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas doodh ka hadiya aa gaya. to aapney unko peechhey se bulwaya , tab hamein tasalli hui ke aap un par (dili taur sey) naraz nahin huey they."
2166,Janab Khilas Hijri kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko bayan kartey huey suna ke main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik hi chadar mein so jatey they halanke main dinon mein hoti. agar aap ko mujh se kuchh (khoon waghaira) lag jata to us jagah ko dho letey aur us jagah se mazeed aagey na dhotey. aur agar aap ke kapdey ko kuch lag jata to usi jagah ko dho letey aur us se tajawuz na kartey aur usi mein Namaz padh letey.
2167,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab apni kisi biwi ke sath letnaa chahtey aur wo haiz se hoti , to usey kehtey ke apni teh band khoob achhi tarah baandh ley , phir uskey sath let jatey."
2168,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se naqal kartey hain ke wo shakhs jo apni biwi se uskey ayyame-haiz mein mujaamiat (sambhog) kar baithey (is ke baabat) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik Dinar sadqa dey ya aadha deenar.'' (hadees peechhey guzar chuki hai dekhiye : 264)
2169,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anha) kehtey hain ke agar khoon ke dino mein mubashrat ki ho to eik Dinar sadqa karey aur agar khoon ruk janey ke dino mein ki ho to aadha deenar.
2170,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney iska zikr aaya yani azl ka , to aapney farmaya : ''tum mein se koi ye karta hi kyon hai? ''aapney ye nahin farmaya : tum mein se koi bhi ye na karey.'' bila-shuba jo jaan paida honey wali hai Allah taala usey paida karkey rahega. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke raawi hadees Qaz'a, ye Ziyad ka maula hai."
2171,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri eik laundi hai aur main us se azl karta hun, aur uska hamila hona mujhey pasand nahin hai, aur main wohi chahta hun jo mard chahtey hain. magar yahudi kehtey hain ke azl karna chhotey andaz mein zinda dargor (qabr mein dafan) karna hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahudi ghalat kehtey hain. agar Allah taala usko paida karna chahega to to usey taal nahin sakta.''"
2172,"Ibne Muhaireez kehtey hain ke main masjid mein dakhil hua aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha to unke paas baith gaya. maine un se azl ke baarey mein puchha , to unhoney kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwae bani mustaliq mein gaey aur hamein us ghazwey mein londiyan haath aaeen, arab aurten, hamein aurton ki bahut khahish thi , aur aurton ke baghair (akele) rehna hamein bahut mushkil ho raha tha. aur ham in laundiyon ko bechnaa bhi chahtey they (is liye chahtey they ke hamila na hon) to ham ne azl ka irada kiya. phir ham ne socha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham mein mojud hain, un se puchhey baghair ham ye kaam keren (kisi tarah jayez nahin). chunanche ham ne aap se is baarey mein puchha , to aapney farmaya : ''agar na karo to tum par koi harj nahin, qiyamat tak jo jaan bhi paida honey wali hai, wo paida ho kar rahegi.''"
2173,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke eik Ansari Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : meri eik londi hai, main us se sohbat karta hun aur uska hamila hona mujhey pasand nahin hai. aapney farmaya : ''agar chaho to azl kar liya karo, jo uskey muqaddar mein hai wo to aa kar rahega.'' bayan kiya ke kuchh din guzrey , phir wo aadmi aap ke paas aaya aur bataya ke londi hamila ho gaee hai. aapney farmaya : ''maine tumhen kaha tha ke jo uskey muqaddar mein hai wo aa kar rahega.''"
2174,"Abu-Nazara bayan kartey hain ke qabeela tufaawa ke eik shaikh ne mujh se bayan kiya ke main Madiney mein Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka mehman hua . wo as-haabe Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein sab se badh kar ibadat mein mustaid aur mehman nawaz they. eik din main unke paas tha jabke wo apney takht par baithey they aur unke paas eik thaili thi, us mein kankariyaan thin ya guthliyaan, takht se nichey unki londi bethi thi siyah rang ki, aap in kankariyon ya guthliyon par tasbih padh rahey they. jab wo khatam ho jati to wo usey uski taraf phenk detey aur wo unhen ikhatti karkey phir se thaili mein bhar kar unko dey deti . Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya main tumhen apni aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baat na sunaun, maine kaha : kyon nahin ! kaha : eik dafa main bukhar mein mubtala masjid mein pada tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye yahan tak ke masjid mein dakhil huey aur puchha : ''kisi ko dosi jawan ki khabar hai?'' (dos Hazrat Abu-Huraira ke qabiley ka naam hai.) aapney teen baar puchha , to eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo masjid ke koney mein hai aur bukhar mein phank raha hai. aap chaltey huey merey paas tashrif laye aur apna haath Mubarak mujh par rakha aur merey baarey mein achhi baat farmaee, to main uth baitha. aur aap chaltey huey apni jaey Namaz par aagey aur namaaziyon ki taraf mutawajjeh huey. aap ke sath do safein mardon ki thin aur eik saf aurton ki ya do safein aurton ki aur eik mardon ki. isliye aapney farmaya : ''agar shaitan mujhey meri Namaz bhulwaa dey to mard Subhanallah kahen aur aurten taali se mutanabbeh (aagah) keren.'' chunanche Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhaai aur Namaz mein se kuchh na bhooley. phir farmaya : ''apni apni jagah baithey raho. apni apni jagah baithey raho.'' Musa ne yahan izafa kiya aur kaha : phir aapney Allah taala ki hamd w sanaa bayan farmaee. phir kaha : Amma-baad ! aur mardon ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur kaha : ''kya tum mein koi hai ke jab apni biwi ke paas jaey, us par darwaza band kar ley , us par parda dal dey aur Allah ke pardey se chup jaey?'' sab ne kaha : ji haan ! aapney farmaya : '' phir wo baitha kehney lagta hai maine aisey kiya, maine aisey kiya.'' to sab khamosh rahey. phir aap aurton ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''kya tum mein koi hai jo ye baaten bayan karti ho?'' to wo khamosh rahin. magar eik naujawan aurat , apney eik ghutney par uthi. Moammal ne apni riwayat mein kaha ke uska seena ubhraa hua tha. usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf gardan lambi ki taake aap usko dekh lein aur uski baat sunen. wo boli : aey Allah ke Rasool ! yaqinan ye mard baaten kartey hain aur ye aurten bhi baaten karti hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya jantey ho iski kya misal hai? '' phir farmaya : ''iski misal us shaitan aurat ki si hai jisey gali mein koi shaitan mard mil jaey aur wo us se apni hajat puri karey aur log uski taraf dekh rahey hon. khabrdar ! mardon ki khushbu ye hai ke uski khushbu zahir ho magar rang zahir na ho aur aurton ki khushbu ye hai ke uska rang numaya ho magar khushbu zahir na ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : is maqam par mujhey Moammal aur Musa se yaad hai. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya :) ''khabrdar ! koi mard kisi mard ke sath na letey ya koi aurat kisi aurat ke sath na letey, siwaey iske ke beta ho ya baap.'' aur teesri baat bhi zikr ki jo mujhey bhool gaee hai aur wo Musaddad ki riwayat mein hai magar wo mujhey kama hiqqa yaad nahin hai. Musa ne apni sanad mein kaha : ''(حدثنا حماد an الجريري an أبي نضرة an الطفاوي).''"
